<p>
  <span class="nym">Gervais</span>
  <span class="gen">m.</span>
  
  <span class="etym"><span class="lang">Old High German, Old Saxon</span> <i>gēr</i> 'spear' + an uncertain element.
  </span>
  
</p>
  
<div class="usg">
  <p>The name of a 2nd C saint.</p>
</div>
  
  
  


